OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMorning low cloud will quickly
OL,6,Fburn away to leave another widely dry
OL,7,Fand sunny day. A little fair weather
OL,8,Fcloud may bubble up later, especially
OL,9,Ftowards the southeast. Breezy over the
OL,10,Fhills but feeling very warm in shelter.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA fine and dry evening will
OL,13,Flead to a largely clear night. Some
OL,14,Fpatchy low cloud may develop later,
OL,15,Fmainly in the east. A warm night,
OL,16,Fespecially in the cities.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
